objectives
write a FSM for the problem mentioned below and implement the the roblem.
problem statement
in the entrance of the car parking system there is a sensor which is activated to detect a vehicle coming.
once the sensor is triggered,a password is requested to open the gate
if the enetered password is correct, the gate would open to let the vehicle get in.
otherwise, the gate is still locked.
if the current car is getting in the car park being detected by the exit sensor and another tye car comes, the door will b locked and requires the coming car to enter the password.
